### 🎯 命名规范

- **组件**: PascalCase (`SnowDayCalculator`)
- **函数**: camelCase (`calculateProbability`)
- **常量**: SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE (`API_BASE_URL`)
- **CSS类**: kebab-case (`search-section`)

